# MonkeDAO Discord Bot

Discord bot that removes reactions on specific channels based on specific roles.

When a user reacts on a message in channel "#test", the bot will check the user's role and if they have a given role it will remove their reaction.

There is "/clean-reactions" command that allow admins to cleanup reactions at any point in time based on user roles.

## Prequesites
- Python 3

## How to run

1. Add `.env`

```bash
DISCORD_TOKEN=YourDiscordTokenHere
DISCORD_CHANNEL=test
DISCORD_ROLE=Member
```

2. Install dependencies
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

3. Run `bot.py`


